      • setServiceConfig

        public MiniCluster.Builder setServiceConfig(String name,
                                   String value)
        Service configs are dynamic config name-value pairs that can be interpreted by the services. This allows new services to be added that have their own encapsulated configuration parameters that don't need to be exposed statically from this Builder.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the configuration parameter
        value - The value of the config setting
        Returns:
        this Builder for method chaining.
